# Internal docs

Working documentation for **__GEM_NAME__** that is *not* shipped in the packaged gem: planning
specs and plans (e.g. superpowers `specs/` and `plans/`), design notes, and other agent/contributor
scratch. The gemspec excludes `internal-docs/` from `spec.files`, so nothing here reaches consumers.

Reserve the top-level `docs/` directory for user-facing documentation (a docs site, guides) when the
gem grows one — that content DOES ship. Keep internal working docs here instead.
